Hello FIRST community,

I’m thrilled to announce the launch of our new team website, designed to be a powerful resource for all teams. Our site features seamless integration with the Blue Alliance API, providing users with the ability to search for any team and any match effortlessly enabling easy access to full team, event, and match history and statistics.

Key Features:

  • Search Any Team: Quickly find information about any FIRST team, including their history, events, and awards.
  • Event data: All event information, including a countdown, registered teams, bracket, leaderboard and math list are easily accessible.
  • Match Data: Access detailed information about matches, including scores, alliances, and outcomes.
  • User-Friendly Interface: Designed for ease of use, our website ensures you can find the information you need with minimal effort.

How to Use:

  1. Search for a Team: Enter the team number or name in the search bar to view detailed information about the team.
  2. Search for a Event: Enter the event to access comprehensive match data.

We believe this tool will be incredibly useful for teams preparing for competitions, scouting, or simply staying informed about the broader FIRST community.

Check out the website frc7790.com

Thanks so much to the team members who are part of Avexel and worked incredibly hard in designing this website.

We welcome your feedback and suggestions to make this tool even better. Let us know what you think!
